If @_mr.va_ wins here, he’s putting the whole welterweight division on notice!

node.text:
Glute leg raises on my BaseBench Pro by @baseblocks!

Make sure you keep your hips perpendicular to the floor and point your toes. Switch it up by changing the elastic settings between sets. Remember to keep the maximum muscular contraction during the peak of your movement!

Link in my bio to check out the equipment.

No excuse!!

node.text:
Here’s the proof that some of the old school fighters are still training 😁 @yves.jabouin is one of the fighters that participated in my very first amateur MMA gala in 2000, when the sport was still very controversial here in Quebec. Click the link in my bio to check out my fight!

Attention, voici la preuve qu’il y a encore quelques-uns des combattants de la vieille école qui s’entraînent toujours 😁. @yves.jabouin fait parti des combattants avec qui j’ai participé à mon premier gala de combat MMA amateur quand le sport était très controversé au Québec en 2000. Cliquez sur le lien dans ma bio pour voir mon combat!
